channel.title: Client help!
channel.description:
Alright, so i've changed some names in the client.java of this client to my server name. But after i had changed them all, it still won't let me connect to my server. But before i changed them, it let me.
Does anybody know why?
I'm getting a error connection to server, and even when i compile it, it says no errors..
Im using Int Dub Pk Client also

item.title: Client help!
item.dc:creator: @thuqs_range2 thuqs range
item.description:
@thuqs_range2 wrote:

disturbing:

You might have changed an ip or link to cache download by accident if the link had the same name as the server

Fixed it, it was my port forwarding.
I typed 5 accidenty instead of 4.
